execute

public java.lang.String execute()
                         throws com.sun.star.uno.Exception
Available devices are looked up, labels are set, and the dialog is executed. It is disposed when the user presses OK or Cancel.

Returns:
The name of the selected embosser device, or an empty String if the dialog was canceled.
